# CineStream - Project Prompt

## Project Goal

Build a full-stack movie recommendation platform where users can:

* Search movies
* Save favorite movies
* Write reviews
* Upload profile images
* Store data permanently in MongoDB Atlas

---

## Functional Requirements

### Movie Search

* Integrate TMDB API
* Display popular movies
* Search movies by title

### Favorites

* Add favorite movies
* Remove favorite movies
* Store favorites in MongoDB

### Reviews

* Create reviews
* Read reviews
* Delete reviews

### User Profile

* Upload profile image
* Store image in Cloudinary
* Save user details in MongoDB

---

## Technical Requirements

### Frontend

* React.js
* Vite
* Tailwind CSS
* Axios
* React Router

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB Atlas
* Mongoose
* Multer
* Cloudinary

### Deployment

* Frontend: Vercel
* Backend: Render
* Database: MongoDB Atlas

---

## API Modules

### Profile API

* Upload profile
